---
title: Crumbed Pumpkin Bites with Sage & Parmesan | Serves 2
description: We've worked out how to improve the classic side dish of golden roasted pumpkin bites – add a crunchy topping of panko breadcrumbs, garlic, sage and Parmesan! Trust us, once you've tried this jazzed-up version there's no going back.

*Unfortunately, this week's pumpkin wedges were in short supply, so we've replaced them with peeled & chopped pumpkin. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
